14:16.724 --> 14:18.026
thing up here. I had four hospitals here, and that 
helped me on that. I branched out, and I had a

14:24.355 --> 14:29.402
partnership and so forth. But when I sold those, 
that's my retirement. And it's... And so that's

14:34.814 --> 14:37.417
the economics part of it. That's important. And I 
raised that question with Calvin Price and

14:38.599 --> 14:44.727
several people, you know, and apparently the 
curriculum... I had Texas Tech, too. I had a

14:45.628 --> 14:50.154
good... That was one reason I asked for it up there. 
