14:50.575 --> 14:54.960
apparently, for anything like that. I think 
that's a real one. Oh, it's where a big lot of

14:56.022 --> 14:58.425
them... their education, I think. So how long were 
you in Longview? About two years, probably two

15:02.851 --> 15:04.933
years. So you set up a practice that you could 
actually sell in two years. That's pretty good.

15:09.698 --> 15:10.919
Yeah, yeah. That's pretty good. I didn't ask 
enough because it sold too quick, but it sold to a

15:11.600 --> 15:23.672
fella in Kilgore that had a practice over there and 
knew, he grew up in Longview, in Marshall, so he

15:11.600 --> 15:23.672
knew the area. We were good friends.

