I looked around and tried to go into Dallas. And you 
saw without knowing where you were going? No,

15:36.638 --> 15:38.019
that's right. You were very brave. Well, 
hard-headed maybe. But anyway, Dallas was nearly

15:42.464 --> 15:49.831
a closed city as far as building veterinary 
hospitals. You had to find some

15:49.851 --> 15:57.218
county land inside Dallas to get the zoning right 
to build a hospital. And so I looked at court work,

16:01.371 --> 16:09.941
which really I loved more than I did Dallas, but 
thought there was more opportunity over there.

16:11.383 --> 16:27.002
