17:58.242 --> 18:12.258
would qualify, and then the city adopted that

17:58.242 --> 18:12.258
building along, and I was able to do what I wanted 
to. So you come on over to Fort Worth? Yes, and I

18:14.080 --> 18:16.123
worked in Dallas. And then you go to the hospital 
right away? I worked in Dallas for about three

18:17.665 --> 18:26.595
months, but then I built my hospital and my home. on 
the west side of Ridgely area. And you're probably

18:30.626 --> 18:34.632
unique again, and you've got capital to start out 
with. Well, I used my ranch to... You got some

18:34.852 --> 18:39.338
credit. ...as equity. My father died when I was 12. 
