20:27.754 --> 20:35.662
family. Your social security is just a drop in the 
bucket. Let me go back and pick up a child. Yeah, go

20:45.152 --> 20:51.419
ahead, because your father died when you were 
young, and your mother is running the ranch. Yeah.

